paths: Obvious paths: north, east, south, northwest
description: The crisscrossing paths which connect the space between tiny huts cease to the northwest, as if fear keeps the huts from being built any closer to the Great Spider, whose dome and gates loom near.  Pine-scented forest breezes buffet you with their unnaturally penetrating chill, causing you to shiver.
title: [Lower Trollfang, Near Shrine]
